	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Perhaps you should look at how games that don't work in your emulator draw sprites. Compare some games that use DMA and some that use direct writes to $2004. You may find that the DMA ones act a certain way while the ones that directly store writes to $2004 act differently.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


