		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As Dwedit said twice, there is nothing wrong with the sprites, it is the background that is wrong.  The distance from top of pict to top of sprites is the same in both pictures.  The distance form the top of pict to the top of the ground is different.  Visibly you can see more brown under the grass on the incorrect screenshot.  Sprite position is correct, background position (likely scrolling) is wrong.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


